text: Gonocerus is a genus of squash bugs belonging to the family Coreidae.BiolibFauna europaea ==Species== * Gonocerus acuteangulatus (Goeze, 1778) * Gonocerus insidiator (Fabricius, 1787) * Gonocerus juniperi Herrich-Schäffer, 1839 * Gonocerus lictor Horváth, 1879 * Gonocerus longicornis Hsiao, 1964 * Gonocerus lux Van Reenen, 1981 * Gonocerus nigrovittatus Ren, 1984 * Gonocerus rex Van Reenen, 1981 * Gonocerus schoutedeni Van Reenen, 1981 * Gonocerus yunnanensis Hsiao, 1964 ==References== Category:Gonocerini Category:Coreidae genera
